    <note>Su(1) Shunyuan [1505] His ancestors were Fufeng jun Su(1). Qi's [1490] son, Yijian's [8115] grandson, Shunqin's [7064] and Shunbin's [7065] brother, Zhuan's [1497] and Xie's [1501] father, Yi's [1502] and Bi's [7340] uncle. His wife's funerary inscription uses a different character for son #5, Hong, and adds a son Ji between Hong and the youngest son, Wen (these sons not in dataset). Sichuan TZ, 122.13b; XCB, 171.9b; SS, 442.13a; Cai Xiang, WJ, 39.1a-5a; Su Shi, W J, 'xu,' 12.392-3 (wife, born Liu, who married him at age 17 and died in 1085 at age 81). CBD, 5, 4342-3.</note>
